('What they say about us', 0, '<p><strong>Praise for Cuoco cookbook:</strong>-</p>\r\n<p>Good work - Vi<img style="background-image: url(http://www.casa-margherita.com/admin/includes/rte/editor/skins/default/fck_strip.gif); background-position: 0px -304px; " class="TB_Button_Image" alt="" src="http://www.casa-margherita.com/admin/includes/rte/editor/images/spacer.gif" />ncent Scordo, Scordo.com</p>\r\n<p>Full of love and passion for our region and its culinary traditions - DiscoveringUmbria blog</p>\r\n<p>I made the semifreddo last night for our guests. They were stunned. - Rupert Kirby, Chef.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Other Comments:-</strong></p>\r\n<p>It has arrived! It is beautiful - thank you very much. Katie Folwell-Davies - London</p>\r\n<p>This is one of the greatest gifts I have ever given-it is on my Christmas list this year also! and I want to thank you for your wonderful and timely follow-up, and of course,&nbsp; excellent olive oils. - Lauren Oates - Michigan</p>\r\n<p><!--StartFragment--><span style="font-size: 12px; ">I just received the package and have to compliment you on your presentation; what great packaging! My father is going to LOVE this, I can&#39;t wait to give it to him. You and your company just made my Christmas holiday even more special so thank you! - Monica N. - USA<br />\r\n</span><!--EndFragment--></p>\r\n<p>Olio arriva... Opened it last night. Lovely! It had quite a  peppery kick more than I remembered from last year. Great stuff and it  went into last night&#39;s salad beautfiully!&nbsp; M Lewis - Beckenham</p>\r\n<p>OLIVE MAGAZINE (BBC GOOD FOOD)<br />\r\nTry Casa Margherita&#39;s gorgeous olive based products from Umbria. Made using moraiolo, leccino and frantoio olives, they produce delicious extra-virgin oils available to buy in 250ml all the way up to three-litre tins</p>\r\n<p>What fantastic service, not only a beautiful original gift you  offer, but your service is first class. - Lesley Halliwell, Dorset</p>\r\n<p>It&#39;s just delicious - a real taste of Umbria permeates - Maxine Levy, London</p>\r\n<p>Thanks for a great birthday present - Deedee Kullenberg, USA</p>', 10, '', '', '', 10, 0, '', 0),
