('/en/home.inc.php', 'a:6:{s:7:"enabled";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:26:"Welcome to Casa Margherita";s:4:"copy";s:3461:"<p>Here at <strong>Casa Margherita</strong> we are passionate about our <strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/olive-oil/oliveoil.html">olive oil</a></strong>. We use organic methods and hand tend our <strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/adopt-tree/index.html">olive trees</a></strong> here in <strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/umbria/index.html">Umbria</a></strong> in the heart of Italy. The <strong>olives</strong> are cold pressed and the oil unfiltered. Our <strong>extra virgin olive oil</strong> (EVO) has a wonderful grassy flavour with a distinctly peppery finish. Buy our pure <strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/olive-oil/oliveoil.html">extra virgin olive oil</a></strong> and taste the difference or try our <strong>flavoured olive oils</strong> made with <a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/condiments-more/basil-flavoured-olive-oil/prod_17.html"><strong>Basil</strong><strong>,</strong></a> <strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/olive-oil/chilli-infused-extra-virgin-oil.html">Chilli</a></strong> and <strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/olive-oil/lemon-infused-extra-virgin-oil.html">Lemon</a></strong> they look beautiful in the kitchen and taste even better!</p>\r\n<p>Why not <strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/adopt-tree/index.html">adopt an olive tree</a></strong> for someone you love - it makes an unusual gift that lasts a whole 12 months - our <strong>adopt a tree</strong> scheme is ideal for someone who loves the Italian life and offer the chance for the adoptee to drizzle their very own <b>olive oil</b> on whatever they fancy. For other great gift ideas have a look at our <strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/olive-oil/gift-boxes/index.html">gift boxes </a></strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/olive-oil/gift-boxes/index.html"><strong>or buy an</strong></a><strong><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/olive-oil/kitchen-accessories/Olive-tree-etching.html"> olive tree etching</a></strong>.</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); "><strong><span style="font-size: medium; ">New! The Casa Margherita cookbook - Cuoco. Packed full of Umbrian recipes.&nbsp;</span></strong></span><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/accessories/casa-margherita-cookbook/prod_22.html"><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0); "><strong><span style="font-size: medium; ">Go to Cuoco now.</span></strong></span></a></p>\r\n<p>So go on.... you know you want to - share our passion!</p>\r\n<div style="padding-bottom: 100px;" class="noborder">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center><img width="0" height="0" alt="" src="/images/uploads/hompage_adopt.jpg" /><a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/adopt-a-tree/cat_6.html"><img width="200" height="201" alt="" src="/images/uploads/hompage_adopt.jpg" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/accessories/casa-margherita-cookbook/prod_22.html"><img width="200" height="268" alt="" src="/images/uploads/homepage_cuoco.jpg" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a href="http://www.casa-margherita.com/olive-oil/cat_2.html"><img width="120" height="200" alt="" src="/images/uploads/homepage_oil.jpg" /></a><br />\r\n</center>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; "><a href="http://www.stradaoliodopumbria.it"><img width="80" height="85" alt="" src="/images/uploads/Strada_logo.gif" /></a></p>\r\n</div>";s:13:"doc_metatitle";s:0:"";s:12:"doc_metadesc";s:0:"";s:16:"doc_metakeywords";s:0:"";}'),
('/it/home.inc.php', 'a:6:{s:7:"enabled";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:27:"Benvenuto a Casa Margherita";s:4:"copy";s:1998:"<p>Casa Margherita non &egrave; solo casa nostra ma anche un uliveto al centro del cuore verde dell&rsquo;<strong>Umbria</strong>, a <strong>Trevi,</strong> la capitale dell&rsquo;olio.</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;Umbria risulta tra i migliori produttori dell&rsquo;olio di oliva in Italia e non a caso &egrave; l''unica regione i cui confini coincidono con quelli della zona di cultivazione&nbsp;<strong> DOP</strong> ( a Denominazione d&rsquo;Origine Protetta).</p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;uliveto di <strong>Casa Margherita</strong> sorge a 465 metri s.l.m. in un terreno molto roccioso che si affaccia verso sud ovest godendo del calore del sole tutto il giorno.&nbsp; Distamo a una distanza di pi&ugrave; di 800 metri dalle case pi&ugrave; vicine e per questo &egrave; possibile garantire agli olivi i 5 elementi chiave per la qualit&agrave; dell&rsquo;olio: siccit&agrave;, sassi, silenzio, solitudine e sole!</p>\r\n<p><span class="info  style11"><a href="Olio_di_oliva.html"><img width="642" height="159" src="/images/uploads/fruit_landscape.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</a></span></p>\r\n<p>L&rsquo;uliveto non &egrave; molto grande ed &egrave; composto da solo 500 piante del misto tipico Umbro, Moraiolo, Leccino e Frantoio; le ridotte dimensioni, ci consentono di lavorarlo in modo tradizionale, completamente&nbsp; a mano, utilizzando&nbsp; concime <strong>biologico</strong> senza aggiunta di trattamenti con insetticidi.</p>\r\n<p>La raccolta delle olive avviene a &ldquo;brucatura&ldquo;, ci&ograve; &egrave; a mano, usando un pettine (rastrellino) e delle reti sotto le piante.&nbsp; <strong>L&rsquo;olio extra vergine</strong> &egrave; <strong>estratto a freddo</strong> in modo da garantire un profumo intenso e un <strong>sapore fresco e fruttato</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Speriamo veramente che vi piaccia il nostro olio d&rsquo;oliva!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Possiamo spedire gli ordinativi in tutta Italia usando il servizio di pagamento online &ldquo;PAYPAL&rdquo;, lo strumento ideale e sicuro per gli acquisti online.&nbsp;</p>";s:13:"doc_metatitle";N;s:12:"doc_metadesc";N;s:16:"doc_metakeywords";N;}'),
